Error: Error: Pterodactyl Panel Minecraft Server Shows "502 Bad Gateway" Error When Trying To Access The Panel.

Solution: Step 1: Check if the error is site-wide or not by trying to access other websites. If you can access them, then the problem is with the Pterodactyl panel server only.
Step 2: Check if the server is running or not. In case the server is down, start the server again in the terminal or command prompt.
